The crew commander transmits flight information to the passengers:
- Dear passengers, we are at an altitude of 10,000 meters, the speed is 800 km/h, the temperature is overboard... A-a-a-a-ept, you fucked up, a-a-a-aaaaaaa, well, that's it, now it's exactly n%good.
After a few minutes:
- Dear passengers, I apologize. It's just that the flight attendant spilled coffee on my white trousers. You should see what my trousers look like on the front right now...
one of the passengers:
- You should see how my trousers look from the back now...
